org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection

Class StudentEnrollmentSwapSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection.StudentEnrollmentSwapSelection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NeighbourSelection<Request,Enrollment>, InfoProvider<Request,Enrollment>, SolverListener<Request,Enrollment>

    public class StudentEnrollmentSwapSelection
extends Object
implements NeighbourSelection<Request,Enrollment>, InfoProvider<Request,Enrollment>, SolverListener<Request,Enrollment>
    Swap enrollments of different students of a course. This is to improve the enrollment alternativity Enrollment.getPriority() as well as selection preferences Enrollment.percentSelected().

    Version:
    StudentSct 1.3 (Student Sectioning)
